snippet.title: GORDO + ECHOES = !!! - Slime Rancher 1.0.1 Gameplay
snippet.description:
EVER WONDERED WHAT TO DO WITH ALL THOSE ECHOES? Josh plays Slime Rancher and tries to get all gordos on his Slime Ranch to decorate it! He uses a Boom Gordo and Echoes to create AMAZING FIREWORKS! Collecting echoes with the echo net for science is a really fun experiment!

Thanks to The Slimeologist for inspiring this episode:
https://twitter.com/TheSlimeologist/status/911343581557854211

➤Let's Play Slime Rancher Ep 1 and Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLX1cB1BI8l6l5NHJMY4cwnJzYP5dDTUy-

Slime Rancher Download for PC, Mac and Linux:
http://www.slimerancher.com/

Slime Rancher Trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iAfP-JCjrmc

There are 4 NEW slimes coming in the Slime Rancher 0.6.0 update when the glass desert arrives! Josh shows you the Mosaic Slime, Tangle Slime, Dervish Slime and Fire Slime all coming in the new slime rancher update. There's lots of new pictures and gifs to see of the cute dervish slime swirling, mosaic slime on fire and the tangle slime catching chickens in the glass desert!
